Name: Chopper To Hell
About the game: Chopper To Hell is a top down twin stick shooter, where big and large spiders are coming in via portals and your job is to kill them all. The spiders are deadly, but you also get a flame thrower. So, you can burn those scary spiders as much as you want. And dont forget to collect those medkits and ammo boxes.
